The paper discusses the optimization of Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) using a metaheuristic algorithm, which is a common topic in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper also discusses the use of optimization algorithms such as Genetic Algorithm, Particle Swarm Optimization, Simulated Annealing, and Harmony Search, which are commonly used in the sub-category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and swarm intelligence (cs.SI). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.CV, and cs.NE, followed by cs.AI and cs.SI.
